# lake-manifest.json is Lake's LOCKFILE and is deliberately TRACKED.
# Six of this repo's nine deps follow a moving branch (aesop/Qq master,
# batteries/plausible/importGraph/LeanSearchClient main); the manifest is the
# only record of the revs these proofs were actually checked against. Ignoring
# it meant a fresh clone resolved to whatever those branches were that day, and
# CI could not build at all. mcp-seal-dev, seal-host and temporal-logic-lean
# all track theirs.
